            "content_html": "<p><code>(Word) Unknown</code> is actually <code>(Word) Cookie</code>. The official client always seems to send 0 for this value but any value you send here is echoed back in the reply. Note as of writing this comment the reply does not have this field documented. See &lt; <a href=\"https://bnetdocs.org/packet/411/mcp-chardelete\">https://bnetdocs.org/packet/411/mcp-chardelete</a> &gt; for more information.</p>"
